OL,3,CRobert Peston: Why Rayner wants
OL,4,CBurnham as prime minister
OL,6,FSometimes I am a bit thick. Often
OL,7,Fmaybe.
OL,9,FBut I had not quite realised that
OL,10,FAngela Rayner's statement that the PM
OL,11,Fshould allow Andy Burnham back into
OL,12,Fparliament was not a statement about
OL,13,FLabour Party democracy.
OL,15,FIt was Rayner saying she would back
OL,16,FBurnham as and when he runs to be
OL,17,FLabour leader.
OL,19,FOr so I am reliably told, to coin the
OL,20,Fcliche.
OL,26,@|D@Frr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
