OL,3,CRobert Peston: Why Rayner wants
OL,4,CBurnham as prime minister
OL,6,FIn other words, she would not be a
OL,7,Fcandidate in a leadership contest that
OL,8,Fincluded Burnham as a candidate.
OL,10,FThat has been said to me explicitly,
OL,11,Fand it feels important.
OL,13,FSo does that mean she has abandoned
OL,14,Fall ambitions to be prime minister?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
